# Verification Plan
1. Navigate to http://localhost:3000
2. Take a screenshot to inspect the shelves and books
3. Verify:
   - Shelf levels are organically mismatched (asymmetrical heights matching the empty photo).
   - Vertical books are scaled inside using percentage height and leave a cozy gap at the top of each shelf.
   - No book overflows or looks broken/clips out of the shelves.
4. If everything looks good, save the final screenshot and report back.
